{"tid":910867,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB正式沒落, 台慶節目要倒抄返大陸既原創綜藝《幻樂之城》","createTime":"2018-11-21T13:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T13:03:52.000Z","uid":67294,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"05f3b37f626dacf68473731ab91d02351ac8115f","tid":910867,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:00:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P1qFsgCFe40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP1qFsgCFe40&d=sg4kdzOBGnbgirfSeSyDw8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=b2db9488\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P1qFsgCFe40</a><br />\n前日TVB台慶有一段講到好有gimmick, 搵兩套劇既人crossover黎做live既演戲<br />\n<br />\n但其實呢個正正係今年湖南衛視原創綜藝《幻樂之城》既idea, 大家可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bWXwgTRAt-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbWXwgTRAt-I&d=sg4kdzOBGnbgirfSeSyDw8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=e3356d71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bWXwgTRAt-I</a><br />\n《幻樂之城》係講搵專業演員live住拍一段一鏡到底既MV, 全程係直播無剪接<br />\n而TVB台慶果段又係set哂場景再用一鏡到底咁拍出黎, 中間鄭子誠讀白+最後再搵菊梓喬唱歌<br />\n<br />\n唔好話咁橋, live舞台劇TVB之前台慶都無做過, 又會咁岩今年大陸做幻樂之城TVB今年就即刻做live舞台劇?<br />\n同埋普通舞台劇都唔會一鏡到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 底仲要有一路都係移動鏡頭追住拍, 加上最尾搵歌手唱歌<br />\n根本成個idea都係同幻樂之城有9成似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最諷刺係湖南衛視之前比人笑去靠抄韓國綜藝, 今次終於第一次揼本做原創綜藝, 起碼真係搵啲大粒野例如王菲那英呢啲去演, 啲美術又靚<br />\n但TVB就繼續用LCD mon就當係佈景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTVB就抄返大陸轉頭, TVB連大陸都抄埋, 真係三年內執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d969d695a3bd0116a1f80fcb1a1